description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps all the action from Week 10 in the NFL. Is Jameis Winston actually the future at QB in New Orleans? How dangerous are the Cardinals? We're joined by Nick Faldo, CBS lead golf analyst. Plus, we hear back from a caller who correctly predicted this years Masters outcome
